<br>
<br>
1. Kelgor's Might<br>
2. +Evade Buff<br>
3. +Haste Buff<br>
4. Totemic Fear w/ Taunting Call as backup.<br>
5. Repeat Step 4 til mob dies.<br>
<br>
I usually evade 2-4 times per fight with Evade III and the second tier Evade buff, along with the defensive bonus of Taunting Call.  Most times after the Kelgor's Might, I hit 2-3 times for every 1 swing of the mob.  My record so far is 7 Totemic Fears in a row, though I probably would have had 8-9 if the mob hadn't died on the 7th. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
If I find neutral mobs, or mobs I can get behind, I open with Clan's Call/Clan's Might, then start at step 1. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.ameritech.net/users/trevanti/savagebanner5.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kintrik@lighttanksofdaoc>Kintrik</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#000000>(12/14/02 10:43 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm20.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=16.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> trol lsavages tink at low lvls</span><hr size=1> plain and simple with my troll savage fully SCd at lvl 17 i never once get even a double hit. both hands with fire but never a double hit.<br>
