<br>
Since practically all of a Savage's really good damage output styles are based on good defense (evading, mainly, but the parry chain is better than nothing), I am troubled by the number of people who think that Wild Call is a good idea. <p>Harana Nyao - Guinevere - Valkyn Savage<br>
